{"tid":2016222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【消委會】國產膠鑊鏟入油炸一分鐘即變形 特福酸性及酒精下釋出量超標","createTime":"2020-05-14T08:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T09:03:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"51a4287b86583e2981cec0d70b436ac6da86bd6d","tid":2016222,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"消費者委員會針對巿面上各式各樣膠鑊鏟測試，結果在 17 款測試的中式膠鑊鏟中，發現一款「JMJ」的鑊鏟，當鏟頭浸入熱油後一分鐘內已熱熔變形，和產品標示的溫度 220&deg;C 不符。另外兩款「Gastro Max」及「Suncraft」尼龍中式鑊鏟測試後也出現輕微變形，不過仍然可用。而「意美廚」的鑊鏟在物料測試後出現起泡情況。「Daiso」樣本亦於測試後鏟頭物料輕微變色。<br />\n<br />\n測試樣本包括17款中式膠鑊鏟，每個大約售價介乎 12 至 99 元不等，樣本購自百貨公司、超級巿場或生活用品店，除 2 款樣本沒有標示製造物料外，其餘均標示為尼龍、聚酰胺或聚醯胺塑料（polyamide）⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%A2%E8%86%A0%E9%91%8A%E9%8F%9F%E5%85%A5%E6%B2%B9%E7%82%B8%E4%B8%80%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%8D%B3%E8%AE%8A%E5%BD%A2-%E7%89%B9%E7%A6%8F%E9%85%B8%E6%80%A7%E5%8F%8A%E9%85%92%E7%B2%BE%E4%B8%8B%E9%87%8B%E5%87%BA%E9%87%8F%E8%B6%85%E6%A8%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2594%25A2%25E8%2586%25A0%25E9%2591%258A%25E9%258F%259F%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E7%2582%25B8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E5%258D%25B3%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%25BD%25A2-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E7%25A6%258F%25E9%2585%25B8%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%258F%258A%25E9%2585%2592%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%2587%258F%25E8%25B6%2585%25E6%25A8%2599%2F&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7luXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=6986f975\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2594%25A2%25E8%2586%25A0%25E9%2591%258A%25E9%258F%259F%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E7%2582%25B8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E5%258D%25B3%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%25BD%25A2-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E7%25A